snippet.title: American Truck Simulator - Michelin Fan Pack DLC Release
snippet.description:
We're excited to introduce a new lineup of truck & trailer tires, officially authorized by Michelin for American Truck Simulator. We've also incorporated a range of cabin accessories and paint options.

Read more about this DLC on our blog 👉 https://blog.scssoft.com/2023/12/michelin-fan-pack-dlc-release.html
